results.title: Software Engineer - TechCorp
results.snippet:
Join TechCorp as a Software Engineer in Boston. We're a 1000-5000 employee Software company looking for talented professionals.

Key Requirements:
• 3+ years experience in software engineer
• Strong technical skills and problem-solving abilities  
• Experience with modern development practices
• Excellent communication and collaboration skills

What we offer:
• Competitive salary and equity
• Comprehensive health benefits
• 401(k) with company matching
• Flexible work arrangements
• Professional development opportunities
• Boston office with remote options

Join our team and help shape the future of software!
